    <h1>The Interactive Python Interpreter</h1>
    <ul>
        <li>Lets you type code straight in</li>
        <li>Code executed immediately</li>
            <ul><li>Each line is run as soon as you press enter</li></ul>
        <li>Type 'python' in your shell</li>
        <li>Press Ctrl+D to exit</li>
    </ul>
</div>

